{
  "snp3.5:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 3.5 ",
  "snp3.5:0.2": "Māghasutta ",
  "snp3.5:1.1": "Evaṁ me sutaṁ—",
  "snp3.5:1.2": "ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. ",
  "snp3.5:1.3": "Atha kho māgho māṇavo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṁ sammodi. ",
  "snp3.5:1.4": "Sammodanīyaṁ kathaṁ sāraṇīyaṁ vītisāretvā ekamantaṁ nisīdi. ",
  "snp3.5:1.5": "Ekamantaṁ nisinno kho māgho māṇavo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "snp3.5:2.1": "“Ahañhi, bho gotama, dāyako dānapati vadaññū yācayogo; ",
  "snp3.5:2.2": "dhammena bhoge pariyesāmi; ",
  "snp3.5:2.3": "dhammena bhoge pariyesitvā dhammaladdhehi bhogehi dhammādhigatehi ekassapi dadāmi dvinnampi tiṇṇampi catunnampi pañcannampi channampi sattannampi aṭṭhannampi navannampi dasannampi dadāmi, vīsāyapi tiṁsāyapi cattālīsāyapi paññāsāyapi dadāmi, satassapi dadāmi, bhiyyopi dadāmi. ",
  "snp3.5:2.4": "Kaccāhaṁ, bho gotama, evaṁ dadanto evaṁ yajanto bahuṁ puññaṁ pasavāmī”ti? ",
  "snp3.5:3.1": "“Taggha tvaṁ, māṇava, evaṁ dadanto evaṁ yajanto bahuṁ puññaṁ pasavasi. ",
  "snp3.5:3.2": "Yo kho, māṇava, dāyako dānapati vadaññū yācayogo; ",
  "snp3.5:3.3": "dhammena bhoge pariyesati; ",
  "snp3.5:3.4": "dhammena bhoge pariyesitvā dhammaladdhehi bhogehi dhammādhigatehi ekassapi dadāti …pe… satassapi dadāti, bhiyyopi dadāti, bahuṁ so puññaṁ pasavatī”ti. ",
  "snp3.5:3.5": "Atha kho māgho māṇavo bhagavantaṁ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi—",
  "snp3.5:4.1": "“Pucchāmahaṁ gotamaṁ vadaññuṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:4.2": "(iti māgho māṇavo) ",
  "snp3.5:4.3": "Kāsāyavāsiṁ agahaṁ carantaṁ; ",
  "snp3.5:4.4": "Yo yācayogo dānapati gahaṭṭho, ",
  "snp3.5:4.5": "Puññatthiko yajati puññapekkho; ",
  "snp3.5:4.6": "Dadaṁ paresaṁ idha annapānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:4.7": "Kathaṁ hutaṁ yajamānassa sujjhe”. ",
  "snp3.5:5.1": "“Yo yācayogo dānapati gahaṭṭho, ",
  "snp3.5:5.2": "(māghāti bhagavā) ",
  "snp3.5:5.3": "Puññatthiko yajati puññapekkho; ",
  "snp3.5:5.4": "Dadaṁ paresaṁ idha annapānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:5.5": "Ārādhaye dakkhiṇeyyebhi tādi”. ",
  "snp3.5:6.1": "“Yo yācayogo dānapati gahaṭṭho, ",
  "snp3.5:6.2": "(iti māgho māṇavo) ",
  "snp3.5:6.3": "Puññatthiko yajati puññapekkho; ",
  "snp3.5:6.4": "Dadaṁ paresaṁ idha annapānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:6.5": "Akkhāhi me bhagavā dakkhiṇeyye”. ",
  "snp3.5:7.1": "“Ye ve asattā vicaranti loke, ",
  "snp3.5:7.2": "Akiñcanā kevalino yatattā; ",
  "snp3.5:7.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:7.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:8.1": "Ye sabbasaṁyojanabandhanacchidā, ",
  "snp3.5:8.2": "Dantā vimuttā anīghā nirāsā; ",
  "snp3.5:8.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:8.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:9.1": "Ye sabbasaṁyojanavippamuttā, ",
  "snp3.5:9.2": "Dantā vimuttā anīghā nirāsā; ",
  "snp3.5:9.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:9.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:10.1": "Rāgañca dosañca pahāya mohaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:10.2": "Khīṇāsavā vūsitabrahmacariyā; ",
  "snp3.5:10.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:10.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:11.1": "Yesu na māyā vasati na māno, ",
  "snp3.5:11.2": "Khīṇāsavā vūsitabrahmacariyā; ",
  "snp3.5:11.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:11.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:12.1": "Ye vītalobhā amamā nirāsā, ",
  "snp3.5:12.2": "Khīṇāsavā vūsitabrahmacariyā; ",
  "snp3.5:12.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:12.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:13.1": "Ye ve na taṇhāsu upātipannā, ",
  "snp3.5:13.2": "Vitareyya oghaṁ amamā caranti; ",
  "snp3.5:13.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:13.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:14.1": "Yesaṁ taṇhā natthi kuhiñci loke, ",
  "snp3.5:14.2": "Bhavābhavāya idha vā huraṁ vā; ",
  "snp3.5:14.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:14.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:15.1": "Ye kāme hitvā agahā caranti, ",
  "snp3.5:15.2": "Susaññatattā tasaraṁva ujjuṁ; ",
  "snp3.5:15.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:15.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:16.1": "Ye vītarāgā susamāhitindriyā, ",
  "snp3.5:16.2": "Candova rāhuggahaṇā pamuttā; ",
  "snp3.5:16.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:16.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:17.1": "Samitāvino vītarāgā akopā, ",
  "snp3.5:17.2": "Yesaṁ gatī natthidha vippahāya; ",
  "snp3.5:17.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:17.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:18.1": "Jahitvā jātimaraṇaṁ asesaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:18.2": "Kathaṅkathiṁ sabbamupātivattā; ",
  "snp3.5:18.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:18.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:19.1": "Ye attadīpā vicaranti loke, ",
  "snp3.5:19.2": "Akiñcanā sabbadhi vippamuttā; ",
  "snp3.5:19.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:19.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:20.1": "Ye hettha jānanti yathā tathā idaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:20.2": "Ayamantimā natthi punabbhavoti; ",
  "snp3.5:20.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:20.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.5:21.1": "Yo vedagū jhānarato satīmā, ",
  "snp3.5:21.2": "Sambodhipatto saraṇaṁ bahūnaṁ; ",
  "snp3.5:21.3": "Kālena tamhi habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.5:21.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha”. ",
  "snp3.5:22.1": "“Addhā amoghā mama pucchanā ahu, ",
  "snp3.5:22.2": "(iti māgho māṇavo) ",
  "snp3.5:22.3": "Akkhāsi me bhagavā dakkhiṇeyye; ",
  "snp3.5:22.4": "Tvañhettha jānāsi yathā tathā idaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:22.5": "Tathā hi te vidito esa dhammo. ",
  "snp3.5:23.1": "Yo yācayogo dānapati gahaṭṭho, ",
  "snp3.5:23.2": "Puññatthiko yajati puññapekkho; ",
  "snp3.5:23.3": "Dadaṁ paresaṁ idha annapānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:23.4": "Akkhāhi me bhagavā yaññasampadaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.5:24.1": "“Yajassu yajamāno, ",
  "snp3.5:24.2": "(māghāti bhagavā) ",
  "snp3.5:24.3": "Sabbattha ca vippasādehi cittaṁ; ",
  "snp3.5:24.4": "Ārammaṇaṁ yajamānassa yañño, ",
  "snp3.5:24.5": "Ettha patiṭṭhāya jahāti dosaṁ. ",
  "snp3.5:25.1": "So vītarāgo pavineyya dosaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:25.2": "Mettaṁ cittaṁ bhāvayamappamāṇaṁ; ",
  "snp3.5:25.3": "Rattindivaṁ satatamappamatto, ",
  "snp3.5:25.4": "Sabbā disā pharati appamaññaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.5:26.1": "“Ko sujjhati muccati bajjhatī ca, ",
  "snp3.5:26.2": "Kenattanā gacchati brahmalokaṁ; ",
  "snp3.5:26.3": "Ajānato me muni brūhi puṭṭho, ",
  "snp3.5:26.4": "Bhagavā hi me sakkhi brahmajjadiṭṭho; ",
  "snp3.5:26.5": "Tuvañhi no brahmasamosi saccaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:26.6": "Kathaṁ upapajjati brahmalokaṁ jutima”. ",
  "snp3.5:27.1": "“Yo yajati tividhaṁ yaññasampadaṁ, ",
  "snp3.5:27.2": "(māghāti bhagavā) ",
  "snp3.5:27.3": "Ārādhaye dakkhiṇeyyebhi tādi; ",
  "snp3.5:27.4": "Evaṁ yajitvā sammā yācayogo, ",
  "snp3.5:27.5": "Upapajjati brahmalokanti brūmī”ti. ",
  "snp3.5:28.1": "Evaṁ vutte, māgho māṇavo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "snp3.5:28.2": "“abhikkantaṁ, bho gotama …pe… ",
  "snp3.5:28.3": "ajjatagge pāṇupetaṁ saraṇaṁ gatan”ti. ",
  "snp3.5:28.4": "Māghasuttaṁ pañcamaṁ. "
}